    <briefdescription>
<para>Control block for a CMSIS-RTOSv2 mutex. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Application can use manual user-defined allocation for RTOS objects by supplying a pointer to mutex control block. Control block is initiazed within <computeroutput>osMutexNew()</computeroutput>. </para>
